//................... Global.asax ................//

Global.asax :- Global.asax is an optional file which is used to handling higher level application events such as Application_Start, Application_End, Session_Start, Session_End etc. 

//.................. web Config......................//

Web Config :- A configuration file (web.config) is used to manage various settings that define a website.
             

Why using web config file :-
Database connections
Caching settings
Session States
